            "title": "Accidental Damage",
            "description": "<p>In the event of functional accidental damage, the Roberto Coin Prestige service team will carefully assess your case with dedicated attention. If your jewel is deemed repairable, Roberto Coin will cover the related repair costs to restore its original beauty. Should it be considered beyond repair, Roberto Coin may, at its sole discretion, offer a digital voucher to purchase a like-for-like creation or, subject to stock availability, provide a replacement. The final decision to repair or replace remains entirely at Roberto Coin’s discretion.<br/><br/></p>"
